Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:05.85,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Donatus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.31,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Poswell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:08.80,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Linemile.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:09.86,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:10.91,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:12.19,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:13.62,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Willard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.13,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Ripley.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:16.34,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Mechthild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:17.43,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Meiyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:21.86,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I need to use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:46.64,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just give them a pat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:48.52,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,They're your kids, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:51.15,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want them to become monsters like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:56.93,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, if it were something you could "catch" like a cold, I would have become one a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:03.54,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I've witnessed many deaths since gaining this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:11.17,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But I was able to suppress the sadness by telling myself that death is just a speck in the grand scheme of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:18.47,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx98}Whenever I'd witness something beautiful or wondrous, I'd accept this body, thinking it'd give me time to see them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:21.43,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it's always been for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:26.19,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Until I met you and had kids, Trisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:34.69,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I never age, but I'm watching\Nmy kids age and grow like trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:37.70,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrified all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:41.74,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me that I truly am a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:47.65,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:49.21,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, come here for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:51.14,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:56.13,Default,Photo,0000,0000,0000,,Good day, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.26,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,A photographer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.09,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Try to look nice, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.10,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,We've never taken a family portrait before, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:04.95,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But this is so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:15.61,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on to Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.48,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.31,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.41,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Please take the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:24.41,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.42,Default,Photo,0000,0000,0000,,Face this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:32.54,Default,Photo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:38.18,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,You know... someday, I'll turn into a wrinkled old woman who looks like a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:45.08,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how I end up looking, I'll always be happy to take a picture with the family where everyone is smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.20,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,So please... stay with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:52.31,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Don't distance yourself from us and leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:57.69,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt yourself by saying you're a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.95,Default,Photo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:06.20,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Smile, Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:23.37,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to accept this body and continue living like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.35,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But I've changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:35.45,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I want to age and die with Trisha and the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.05,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.01,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.61,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.44,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Fixing the swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.51,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,You're not really used to these things, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:07.55,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do a single thing for them, so I wanted to at least do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:12.81,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Trisha, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.35,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.32,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.82,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell the kids about my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.00,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:27.95,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to say goodbye to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.09,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,If I see their faces, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:35.17,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,You blockhead. It's okay if you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.97,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, why are you two up so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al says he needs to go pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:52.93,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were looking after Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:54.90,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:33.01,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Any luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:12.99,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,No, I still can't reach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:16.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good... we can't contact the guys at base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.45,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,What now? Should we keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:23.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There should be an exit somewhere to toss the rubble that was dug out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep going for just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:27.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Smith, you go back to report on the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:28.59,Default,Smith,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:39.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Spread out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.97,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in a perfect, immortal army?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:22.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.52,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,No death, no decay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.01,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.94,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cut him to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:37.07,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that the idea is so wild; I don't know how to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:41.59,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two choices:\NYou're either interested, or you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:45.76,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I'm intrigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:53.48,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,So when that day comes, not just I,\Nbut my men will also be able to benefit from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.59,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,When that day comes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:59.22,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,So he can't guarantee that much, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:05.78,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,If I accept their offer, they'll force me to assist them in causing a bloodbath at Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:11.73,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,And if I decline, they'll put someone else in charge of the base, and I'll most likely be demoted or reassigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:15.75,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I wonder what my best option is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.24,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:23.80,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to bother you, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The advance unit that went into the underground tunnel-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:30.11,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,What about the underground tunnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.92,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:32.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:35.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Something has happened to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.23,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:38.39,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.12,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to be tied up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:56.71,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this, Buccaneer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:01.92,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently transferring the Elric Brothers from the east cells to the west cells, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:03.79,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that gentleman, if I may ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:06.17,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Solf J. Kimblee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.04,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,He's Lieutenant General Raven's guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee... So he's the Crimson Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:16.80,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,The Elric Brothers... So you must be the Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:20.43,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see why you were given that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.97,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since anyone's made that mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:29.94,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:32.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:39.11,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:42.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost contact with the platoon that went to investigate the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:48.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And soon after, Smith's horse came back with an arm presumed to be his.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:49.88,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Just his arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.08,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,What about his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.76,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Missing, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:57.14,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,The horse he was on is too worked up\Nand can no longer be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.22,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Henshel, send in a rescue party imme-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:03.20,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good, Major General Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:06.10,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,That hole is far too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:10.35,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with that biological weapon you were talking to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.23,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Put him back into the tunnel and\Ncover up the hole, Major General.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.63,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,But our men are still-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.98,Default-alt,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to the Major General.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.21,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the law here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:27.96,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Obey the ones with power, Major General Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.51,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Raven from Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:42.59,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard everything from the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:46.72,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've been keeping your mouths shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We promised, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.39,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:54.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be strange to be happy after having people taken hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:58.40,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... when can we get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:03.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The deal was that we'd be able to continue\Nour journey as long as we didn't get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:06.45,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll get you out of here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:11.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That hole... it's also a part of your plan, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:12.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If they find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.04,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:21.59,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Major General Armstrong agreed to returning\Nthe Homunculus in the tunnel and sealing the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.97,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,The Major General joined forces with us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:30.72,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.66,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we going to search for the missing unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:34.90,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, Henshel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.86,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,But they may still be alive and need assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.28,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I said, silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.15,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:48.03,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,"Obey the ones with power", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:53.45,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,So even the impregnable "Northern Wall of Briggs" has to give in to authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:56.54,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the smart approach to things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:07.59,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So that's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.47,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.19,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.15,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.05,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:23.24,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. You still have some work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.74,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Pride tell you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.74,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,Pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:34.79,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,It's a drag... but I have to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:40.06,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,What a drag...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.63,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,Why was it a drag again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.90,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to remember is a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.28,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:57.89,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,He's a chimera that's performing a task for the Central Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:02.40,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,He's working to make this country stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.80,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still a top-secret mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:10.27,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Now, cover up this hole, my friends at Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:13.11,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,You all are kindred spirits who I've shared my secrets with!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:31.89,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,The essential parts have been replaced with ancient Ishbalan, so I can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.74,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't help that, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.32,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,If Scar were here, we might be able to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:41.30,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,If he's an Ishbalan monk, there's a chance he'd know the ancient language.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:47.51,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened to Mr. Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We've found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A little girl carrying a black and white cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.31,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:07.63,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Scar! Sir Yoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:09.51,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find the research documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.89,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:13.52,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Let's switch locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.86,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers from Briggs have already found this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.02,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.88,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:31.15,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,We, the chosen ones, will be granted a body close to God's, and we'll rule this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:33.79,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Was his name Smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:36.66,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can be done about the advance unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:41.33,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,So the weak should become victims for the chosen ones to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:44.23,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Survival of the fittest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:49.47,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,The weak become the foundations of a nation, and the strong prosper above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.88,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,So Ishbal was also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.16,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:54.67,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Ishbal was also a part of our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:58.39,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Those weak people were destined to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.03,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:05.05,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:06.54,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.41,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:16.59,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly make a lot of phone calls, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.63,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Lieutenant General Raven?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:21.26,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:30.99,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,You were on the verge of death, but you somehow managed to make a recovery on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.19,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of magic spell did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:35.93,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:40.68,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, you were jailed for killing officers. How did you manage to get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:44.32,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.94,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Since when has this plan been in motion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.14,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard it's been in motion since this country was created.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:54.88,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll finally be complete during my generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:58.95,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your cooperation, Major General Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.93,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'll negotiate with the higher-ups and prepare a seat for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:05.29,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.46,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:15.34,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Was that Smith's left arm? Or his right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.47,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:21.81,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Aging is truly horrifying, isn't it, Lieutenant General Raven?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:27.85,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you used to be a young, dignified soldier who loved this country from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.79,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.90,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,You have the chance to become a chosen one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.31,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I promised you a seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:35.99,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for another seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:41.49,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking the seat your rotten ass has been sitting on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.91,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You useless geezer!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:57.09,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Immortality... is right in front of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:03.60,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You can lie there and literally become a foundation of this base, Lieutenant General Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:07.82,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted... to become immortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:12.25,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Buccaneer, contact Miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.00,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:15.31,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else, continue working as if nothing's happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:16.32,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,General.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:16.97,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.82,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Smooth the concrete, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.82,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:26.36,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You're being very pushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:31.74,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm a State Alchemist who served in the Ishbalan War?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:35.40,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do to satisfy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:39.07,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know what kind of deaths your people experienced?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:40.34,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Kimblee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.47,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:44.47,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:47.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:53.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from Major General Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:58.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She says, "Mission complete.\NYou don't need to buy any more time."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.49,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.58,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.16,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I'm relieved from talking with that freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.87,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was putting on an act, it was exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.25,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.04,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Lieutenant General Raven is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.63,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Do you happen to know where he'd be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:17.85,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.58,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:23.64,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,The base isn't built safely enough for people to just walk around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.76,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to the Lieutenant General-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.77,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,That's good for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:37.73,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I received permission from the Führer President to act independently if something happened to Lt. General Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:42.61,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Could you drive me down to the base of the mountain, Major Miles?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.02,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:51.04,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,My orders right now hold equal importance to those of the Führer President's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.40,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:59.99,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Before you cover the hole completely, please send in a search squad for Smith and the unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:06.89,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,The Fullmetal Alchemist created a secret passage in case a situation like this arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,She killed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.77,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant General Raven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.20,Default,Neil,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's all I needed to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,When the hell are you guys going to let us out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:23.53,Default,Neil,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Ask the Major General.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:25.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:27.62,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Getting impatient won't do us any good, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:30.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's more important to rest for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:34.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay put when so many things are going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.02,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:44.37,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to speak with the Fullmetal Alchemist-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:49.75,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It seems as though I'm not very popular here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:53.31,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought a guest today for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.51,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,"Why"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.49,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,To switch your automail to the kind they use up here, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.76,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys in jail, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No one called you out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.98,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:14.75,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:17.59,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have known if the people from the military hadn't told me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.59,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The military?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.59,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:25.13,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President was very worried to hear of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:00.85,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:02.07,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:05.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from a friend who works as a nurse at the foot of Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:07.74,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He was hospitalized with serious injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:12.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,but his wounds were healed right after Lieutenant General Raven came to visit, and he was released right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:15.28,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Raven and Kimblee...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:17.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's about all the information I have for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:20.06,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:22.42,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask for your help again when I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.23,0:23:25.00,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Stop by at the shop again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:30.56,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You were dumped, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:34.24,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you buy some flowers and chase after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:36.65,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I know when to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:38.13,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:41.48,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There are women who will dump you, but there are also women who are looking for a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.54,0:23:45.90,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from\NMajor General Olivier Mira Armstrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:48.50,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Roy Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:54.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be buying all of those flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:24:02.53,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The chain binding them appears in unusual form.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:06.56,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, unbind the chains and wrench them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:09.97,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Reel it in and expose the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.97,0:24:15.05,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:19.62,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 37, The First Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:22.48,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Stratagems and blackmailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:25.40,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the measures taken to fulfill one's desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,0)\an8}13 Years Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(430,0)\an8}A Few Days Later
